                        <pre class="page"><code>1.1.txt, 1.1.3.txt and 1.txt go in                   FileGroup0000000001.zip  <br>11.txt and 11.1.txt goes in                          FileGroup0000000011.zip   <br>2.1.3.6.txt, 2.1.3.6.7.txt, 2.1.txt, and 2.txt go in FileGroup0000000002.zip </code></pre>
